<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV107">
<l>kāyciṉatta kācimaṉṉaṉ vakkaraṉpa vuṇṭiraṉ</l>
<l>māciṉatta mālimāṉcu mālikēci tēṉukaṉ</l>
<l>nācamuṟṟu vīḻanāḷka varntaniṉka ḻaṟkalāl</l>
<l>nēcapāca mettiṟattum vaittiṭēṉem mīcaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Other than for Your feet—that stole the days of the king of Kāśi with a burning rage,</l>
<l>[Dantā]vakra, Pauṇḍra [Vāsudeva], the very angry Mālin, the great Sumālin, Kēśin,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] Dhenuka,</l>
<l>So that they were destroyed and fell—I shall not place [my] attachment and affection</l>
<l rend="indent">Anywhere [else], our Lord!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
